00:30:11.160 --> 00:30:14.160 align:middle line:90%
and closer to our plates.

00:30:14.160 --> 00:30:16.320 align:middle line:84%
To better understand
the question,

00:30:16.320 --> 00:30:18.982 align:middle line:84%
Chelsea visited
many fishmongers.

00:30:18.982 --> 00:30:21.700 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

