00:31:14.350 --> 00:31:16.000 align:middle line:90%
What are the effects?

00:31:16.000 --> 00:31:16.900 align:middle line:90%
What do we know?

00:31:16.900 --> 00:31:19.610 align:middle line:90%


00:31:19.610 --> 00:31:23.960 align:middle line:84%
There are still very few
studies but one of these

00:31:23.960 --> 00:31:24.980 align:middle line:90%
