00:32:35.430 --> 00:32:38.670 align:middle line:90%
it is a very minor vector.

00:32:38.670 --> 00:32:40.770 align:middle line:84%
>> The conclusions
are reassuring,

00:32:40.770 --> 00:32:46.170 align:middle line:84%
