up by the tissue.

00:33:37.880 --> 00:33:43.810 align:middle line:90%


00:33:43.810 --> 00:33:47.800 align:middle line:84%
>> To put it another way, it can
end up in other organs without

00:33:47.800 --> 00:33:49.330 align:middle line:90%
us knowing the consequences.

00:33:49.330 --> 00:33:55.110 align:middle line:90%


00:33:55.110 --> 00:33:57.870 align:middle line:84%
